<!-- ═══════ LANDLORD REP ═══════ -->

<div class="asset">
  <h2>Landlord Rep: Operating as the Leasing Office</h2>

  <p>This is not a referral play. I am the leasing office. Eight buildings. 36 units. Every unit has dual pricing — market rate for walk-in tenants, Section 8 rate for voucher holders. The Section 8 rate is higher because the Housing Authority guarantees the payment. The commission structure reflects this: 75% on market-rate, 100% on Section 8. Every voucher tenant is a priority.</p>

  <pre style="background:#0a0a0a; border:1px solid #222; padding:1.5rem; font-size:0.8rem; line-height:1.6; color:#888; overflow-x:auto; margin:2rem 0;">
