email_monitor.py     Gmail API every 5 minutes → extract attachments
doc_interpreter.py   AI classifies: pay stubs, bank statements, ID, voucher
approval_engine.py   Income ≥ 2.5x rent? Background OK? Docs complete?
asana_ygl.py         Create ticket → assignee: building manager → SLA tracking

# Qualification lanes:
Lane 00: VOUCHER ATTACK       Section 8 + docs → process in 24hrs. 100% commission.
Lane 01: SLAM DUNK            Strong income, good credit, docs near complete.
Lane 02: QUALIFIED             Active, some docs, needs specific remaining items.
Lane 03: WORKS W/ MITIGATION   Qualified but complicating factor (credit, cosigner).
